    "custom_liquid_wDyKqP": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Custom Liquid",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": true,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": true,
        "liquid": "<!-- ═══ FOUNDER STORY ═══ -->\n<div class=\"elorya-founder\">\n  <div class=\"elorya-founder__badge\">Our Story</div>\n\n  <h2 class=\"elorya-founder__title\">I designed the dress I could never find.</h2>\n\n  <div class=\"elorya-founder__image-wrap\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0795/2754/3033/files/35b29f1c-1b78-429f-9759-8fe254494e06_430x.png?v=1784758705\"\n         alt=\"The woman behind ELORYA\" class=\"elorya-founder__image\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    <span class=\"elorya-founder__caption\">The dress that started it all, worn the way I always wanted to wear it.</span>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Texte visible -->\n  <div class=\"elorya-founder__text\">\n    <p>For most of my life, I dreaded summer.</p>\n    <p>Not the season, the getting dressed. I grew up never quite comfortable in my own skin, and every hot day meant the same impossible choice: wear something loose and feel invisible, or wear something fitted and spend all day holding my stomach in. Nothing ever felt like <em>me</em>.</p>\n    <p>By my forties, after two kids and a body that had changed the way bodies do, I'd basically given up. My summer uniform was leggings and an oversized t-shirt, and I'd catch myself in the mirror barely recognizing the woman looking back.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Texte caché + fondu + bouton -->\n  <div class=\"elorya-founder__more\" id=\"founderMore\">\n    <div class=\"elorya-founder__fade\" id=\"founderFade\">\n      <button class=\"elorya-founder__btn\" id=\"founderBtn\">\n        Read the rest of my story\n        <span class=\"elorya-founder__arrow\">⌄</span>\n      </button>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"elorya-founder__hidden\" id=\"founderHidden\">\n      <p>So I started sketching the dress I wished existed.</p>\n      <p>Light enough to forget I was wearing it. Loose where I wanted to hide, so nothing clung to my stomach. Opaque enough to walk out the door without a second thought. And a back I could adjust myself, open when I felt like it, covered when I didn't. Because feeling beautiful shouldn't mean showing more than you're ready to.</p>\n      <p>I spent months on the fabric alone, until I put one on, walked into my kitchen, and my husband stopped mid-sentence. No makeup, wet hair, barefoot. That was the whole point.</p>\n      <p>I didn't build ELORYA for models. I built it for the woman I was at 42, standing in her closet, wanting to feel beautiful without the effort or the compromise. If that's you, this dress was designed for you.</p>\n      <p class=\"elorya-founder__sign\">— The woman behind ELORYA</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.elorya-founder {\n  max-width: 620px;\n  margin: 40px auto;\n  padding: 32px 22px;\n  background: #FDF8F4;\n  border-radius: 16px;\n}\n.elorya-founder__badge {\n  display: inline-block;\n  font-size: 11px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  letter-spacing: 1.2px;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  color: #C4614A;\n  background: #fff;\n  padding: 5px 12px;\n  border-radius: 999px;\n  margin-bottom: 16px;\n}\n.elorya-founder__title {\n  font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;\n  font-size: clamp(24px, 5vw, 32px);\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #1a1a1a;\n  line-height: 1.3;\n  margin: 0 0 22px;\n}\n.elorya-founder__image-wrap { margin: 0 0 24px; }\n.elorya-founder__image { width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; display: block; }\n.elorya-founder__caption {\n  display: block;\n  font-size: 12.5px;\n  font-style: italic;\n  color: #999;\n  margin-top: 8px;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n.elorya-founder__text p,\n.elorya-founder__hidden p {\n  font-size: 15px;\n  color: #444;\n  line-height: 1.75;\n  margin: 0 0 16px;\n}\n.elorya-founder__text em,\n.elorya-founder__hidden em { font-style: italic; color: #1a1a1a; }\n\n/* Zone repliable */\n.elorya-founder__more { position: relative; }\n.elorya-founder__fade {\n  position: relative;\n  height: 90px;\n  margin-top: -80px;              /* remonte le fondu par-dessus le dernier paragraphe visible */\n  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(253,248,244,0) 0%, #FDF8F4 65%);\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: flex-end;\n  justify-content: center;\n  pointer-events: none;\n}\n.elorya-founder__btn {\n  pointer-events: auto;\n  display: inline-flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 8px;\n  background: #fff;\n  border: 1px solid #e8ddd6;\n  color: #1a1a1a;\n  font-size: 14px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  font-family: inherit;\n  padding: 11px 20px;\n  border-radius: 999px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  box-shadow: 0 3px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n  transition: box-shadow 0.2s;\n}\n.elorya-founder__btn:hover { box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12); }\n.elorya-founder__arrow {\n  color: #C4614A;\n  font-size: 16px;\n  transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n.elorya-founder__hidden {\n  max-height: 0;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  transition: max-height 0.5s ease;\n}\n.elorya-founder__sign {\n  font-family: Georgia, serif;\n  font-style: italic;\n  font-size: 15px;\n  color: #C4614A;\n  margin-top: 20px;\n}\n\n/* État ouvert */\n.elorya-founder__more.open .elorya-founder__fade {\n  height: 0;\n  margin-top: 0;\n  background: none;\n}\n.elorya-founder__more.open .elorya-founder__btn { display: none; }\n.elorya-founder__more.open .elorya-founder__hidden { max-height: 1200px; }\n\n@media (max-width: 600px) {\n  .elorya-founder { padding: 26px 18px; margin: 28px auto; }\n}\n</style>\n\n<script>\n(function() {\n  var more = document.getElementById('founderMore');\n  var btn = document.getElementById('founderBtn');\n  btn.addEventListener('click', function() {\n    more.classList.add('open');\n  });\n})();\n</script>",
